com.pb.sawdust.calculator

Class NumericFunctionN.FlexFunctionN

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pb.sawdust.calculator.NumericFunctionN
      • com.pb.sawdust.calculator.NumericFunctionN.FlexFunctionN
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    NumericFunctionN.DecimalFunctionN, NumericFunctionN.IntegralFunctionN
    Enclosing class:
    NumericFunctionN

    public abstract static class NumericFunctionN.FlexFunctionN
extends NumericFunctionN
    The FlexFunctionN provides a skeletal implementation of NumericFunctionN. The only remaining methods that need to be implemented are the apply methods acting on longs and doubles. All apply calls using integer (in the generic sense) arguments will (by default) use the method acting on longs, and all calls using decimal arguments will use the method acting on doubles.
